InvestmentContractTest
├── given investment round is closed
│   └── it should revert with InvestmentContract_InvestmentRoundClosed
├── given amount is below minimum
│   └── it should revert with InvestmentContract_MinimumInvestmentNotMet
├── given insufficient allowance
│   └── it should revert with ERC20: insufficient allowance
└── given valid investment parameters
    ├── when invest is called
    │   ├── it should decrease investor's USDC balance
    │   ├── it should increase contract's USDC balance
    │   ├── it should mint NFT to investor
    │   ├── it should record investment amount
    │   └── it should emit InvestmentMade event
    ├── when withdraw is called
    │   ├── given withdraw caller is not owner
    │   │   └── it should revert with Ownable: caller is not the owner
    │   ├── given contract has insufficient balance
    │   │   └── it should revert with ERC20: transfer amount exceeds balance
    │   └── given valid withdrawal parameters
    │       ├── it should increase owner's USDC balance
    │       └── it should decrease contract's USDC balance
    └── when closeInvestmentRound is called
        ├── given close round caller is not owner
        │   └── it should revert with Ownable: caller is not the owner
        └── given caller is owner
            └── it should set investmentRoundClosed to true
